INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72351, 'The world could use more love. Why deny it to others?', 5744, 0), (72352, 'Time stops for no one, and if we allow ourselves to focus on the negative we might miss out on some really amazing things that life has to offer. We can''t go back to the past, we can only take the lessons that we have learned and the experiences that we have gained from it and move on. It is because of the heartaches, as well as the hardships, that in the end help to make us a stronger person.', 12653, 0), (72353, 'If you are sad, love will make you happy; afraid, love will make you brave; weak, love will make you strong; and broken, love will make you whole.', 5104, 0), (72354, 'Love affords you these three things: smiles, hugs, and kisses. Joy affords you these three things: pleasure, laughter, and good memories.', 5104, 0), (72355, 'There was no slow build. No peaceful meander to the summit. It was like sheet lighting stretching across a stormy sky—beautiful and blinding. I leaned forward and seized his mouth with mine.', 15262, 0), (72356, 'Don’t resent a woman for who she is not', 15263, 0), (72357, 'Cherish simple things such as family, friends and love, because great things appear simple from far away. Place your simple things in the best light; there''s enough sunshine for all of them', 8514, 0), (72358, 'You are a drop of perfect in an imperfect world. and all I need, is a taste', 323, 0), (72359, 'To say her goodbye …!!I knew there was somethingIn wink of your smile In touch of your voiceWith the hurt of good bye Precious moments are not lasting long Controlling my lifeAnd I don’t know whyI won’t see her anymoreFor long …So much to say .. But words are missing & time is running To say her goodbyeThe beauty of imperfect Speechless moment Was not enough for silent tears To way back in this lifeAll my memories Keeps you near brings me far From home …I ll remember ..The silent whisper To say her goodbye..Waving hand to sky … And a kiss to winds I’ll remember..!!Rhitwik', 15264, 0), (72360, 'Love lost is better than hate found. True criticism is better than false praise. Genuine enemies are better than counterfeit friends.', 5104, 0), (72361, 'One who forgives his enemies conquers them', 15265, 0), (72362, 'He isn''t the best, neither am I. But we are the best version of ourselves with each other. And that''s pretty close to Perfection.', 2965, 0), (72363, 'The loudest preacher in the world is your conscience, the cleverest is wisdom, the rowdiest is passion, the surest is truth, the purest is love, and the highest is God.', 5104, 0), (72364, 'Blessing others is easy when done through love', 15266, 0), (72365, 'A man with integrity, with vision, with a sense of purpose and place in the world as exactly himself. That''s the kind of man I''ll settle for.', 3305, 0), (72366, 'The greatest love stories are not written by the ink of the pen, but by the ink of the heart.', 5104, 0), (72367, 'keep love in your heart. A life without is like a sunless garden when the flowers are dead ...', 15160, 0), (72368, 'Not only were my nerves shot, but my body was a traitor. I didn’t want to melt against him. I didn’t want to enjoy the feeling of his lips sliding across my skin. I didn’t want to like the possessive way his fingers dug into my waist or the way his erection pressed against me.', 15262, 0), (72369, 'Ryker smiled at me. “You learn quick—”I cut him off. “If you call me grasshopper, I’m going to slug you.” “Padawan.” I shoved him. It was more like shoving a tree. He didn’t even flinch. “You’re such a nerd.”“Geek, Millie. I’m a geek.” His lips twitched and it made me want to raise myself up on my tiptoes and kiss him. I shot him a grin instead. “Only a nerd would know the difference.', 15262, 0), (72370, 'Stick with me, kid. I’ve got this.” His words were an echo of a promise he made long ago, not long after we first met. He always knew exactly what to say, to do, and that’s the reason I didn’t move away when he brought his lips down to mine. It’s the reason I let my hands slide over his bare chest. They mimicked the way his tongue slid along my lower lip when I sighed and melted into him.', 15262, 0), (72371, 'What is more painful: Unable to get the Love of your life or being Indifference to the One who loves you the most?', 12721, 0), (72372, 'Love is a funny business. It cannot be commanded but it commands us; it commands respect and unselfishness. Love cannot be sucked out of another in the hopes that it fills us up, because love is not a selfish quest.', 15267, 0), (72373, 'You cant Realize Someone Good Is Coming Your Way, if still Remain Sleep on the Fact that they Actually Exist! Wake and smell the Coffee or Excuse yourself if your Nose is a bit Stuffy.', 15268, 0), (72374, 'Love didn''t seem like something that could be organized or contained; it should be messy and emotional, like exploding and imploding with someone at the exact same time.', 15269, 0), (72375, 'Many speak to her but she''s looking for the one who knows her souls language.', 3305, 0), (72376, 'You''re the one I like. Maybe love.', 13290, 0), (72377, 'Love does not wear out the heart, even if it weighs a thousand tons.', 5104, 0), (72378, 'Whenever you feel hatred to your loved ones, start thinking about the love you felt once for your beloved.', 12339, 0), (72379, 'I felt you before I knew of your existence, maybe it was a hint from the universe to continue on the yellow brick road, so when I would find you along my travels I would simply just know.', 3305, 0), (72380, 'Anyway, what I''m trying to say is, I really like you. A lot. But if you don''t feel the same way about me, it''s okay. Because you''re really important to me, and I hope we can still be friends.', 13290, 0), (72381, 'Pleasure can turn the body into a slave.Desire can turn the mind into a fool.Passion can turn the heart into a beast.Love can turn the soul into an angel.', 5104, 0), (72382, 'I miss your voice because it is a symphony', 15270, 0), (72383, 'Love is the name of an irrepressible moment formed inside one complete pulsation of a heart', 2760, 0), (72384, 'You know all my needs and wants, you know hundreds of small things about me! You also know I am madly falling in love with you, You even know when I am staring at you! You know how much I desire you!', 8479, 0), (72385, 'Our eyes met and a never-before feeling entered our hearts. We gazed at each other longingly. We were indeed smitten by each other. Even before we realised, our lips locked. Ah, my first kiss. I had heard stories of how the first kiss is etched in one’s memory forever. This was absolute bliss. I felt a sense of belonging, a sense of togetherness. He took me by surprise with his proposal of love for me. Those magical words still linger in my heart. My dream of finding the right man had become a reality.', 15271, 0), (72386, 'Mind is effort, while heart is effortless! What are YOU?', 12721, 0), (72387, 'No matter how long it takes, true love is always worth a wait, because waiting is the sign of true love....', 8479, 0), (72388, 'Desire speaks, passion shouts, lust screams, and love whispers.', 5104, 0), (72389, 'Only the ones whose hearts have been conquered by LOVE know the secret language of the eyes. Leave trails of love today, perhaps others might be brave enough to follow', 8514, 0), (72390, 'One moment before, I knew nothing of it. And then, all of a sudden, I knew this was it. The most amazing thing. I could feel the whispers, I could feel all the dimensions possible. I could define it. I could call it Love', 9357, 0), (72391, 'As a parting gift, he gave Harold the key chain from his house keys, the ones that opened the gate to Hamilton Arms: it was a clover, a charm for luck. Its stem was a little drawer, into which, Harold later found, George had put a love note. Harold kept the clover for the rest of his life.', 15272, 0), (72392, 'Love. It doesn''t change for any person to any person. It evolves.', 12339, 0), (72393, 'It feels good when the one you owe walks with you. It feels ecstatic when the one you don''t owe walks.', 15273, 0), (72394, 'Hurt me back when I hurt you and I would always love you for it.', 15274, 0), (72395, 'People think that LGBTs adopting children will hurt them, but it''s not being in loving homes that hurts children most.', 5744, 0), (72396, 'What I cannot tough, remains a memory, I am blinded by an imagined light. A remembrance of what can never be', 15133, 0), (72397, 'What I cannot touch, remains a memory. I am blinded by an imagined light. A remembrance of what can never be.', 15133, 0), (72398, 'Life is not made up of minutes, hours, days or years, but of moments. Nothing is permanently perfect. But there are perfect moments.', 12114, 0), (72399, 'Sweet girl, maybe close the world off and look at him for an houror two.This is your fairy. It ain’t perfect and it ain’t honey sweet with roses on the bed.It’s real and raw and ugly at times. But this is your love. Don’t throw it away searching for someone else’s love. Don’t be greedy. Instead, shelter it. Protect it. Capture every second of easy, pull through every storm of hardship. And when you can, look at him, lying next to you, trusting you not to harm him. Trusting you not to go. Be someone’s someone for someone.Be that someone for him.', 523, 0), (72400, 'And I learnt five new languages in the last three years""Only if you could for once understand the language of my eyes.', 7550, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72401, 'What does love mean if we would deny it to others?', 5744, 0), (72402, 'Plucking a rose only proves you desire it, but nurturing it proves you love it.', 5104, 0), (72403, 'He said, I''ve been coming for you on a hard road. I''m never letting you go. Never.', 584, 0), (72404, 'If there’s one thing I’ve learned, buddy, it’s that love is messy and complicated. If it’s too easy, then it isn’t the real deal. It can’t be, because passion doesn’t follow the path of least resistance. It’s this fiery, out-of-control entity that sucks you in and spits you out more hurt and more alive than ever before.', 15205, 0), (72405, 'I want a long life, measured not in days and years but the moments that we spent together', 7550, 0), (72406, 'He saw with sorrow that hers was a life he could step right into and keep working at hard from tonight until death. If he allowed himself to ponder it for a minute, he saw all the world hanging over the girl like the deadfall to a trap, ready to drop and crush.', 584, 0), (72407, 'How they madeout of shamelessness somethingbeautiful, for as long as they could.', 15275, 0), (72408, 'The best relationships are the ones you never saw coming', 8479, 0), (72409, 'Love FREES both the giver and the receiver, love INCLUDES all, love GIVES without seeking or demanding anything in return', 8514, 0), (72410, 'Love frees both the giver and the receiver- FREE someone today... LOVE themLove includes all- INCLUDE someone today... LOVE them Love gives without seeking or demanding anything in return-GIVE to someone today without seeking or demanding... LOVE them', 8514, 0), (72411, 'This story is not about avoiding death, but living life.', 7636, 0), (72412, 'There''s no difficulty that love cannot conquer... no door love cannot open...No wall enough love will not bring down... only if we could love enough When love, skill, a talent or gift work together... we create a masterpieceLove someone with your skill, your talent or our gift... Make someone''s life easier... Make someone happy today... Create your masterpiece today', 8514, 0), (72413, 'Love at first sight kill at first betray', 15276, 0), (72414, 'There are thousands of languages around the world, but love is the most beautiful of them all.', 5104, 0), (72415, 'You spend the beginning part of your life with your mother, so love her; the middle part of your life with your girlfriend, so care for her; and the end part of your life with your wife, so adore her.', 5104, 0), (72416, 'When love writes a letter, joy is its ink.', 5104, 0), (72417, 'If your soul mate comes with too much baggage, help her unpack it.', 5104, 0), (72418, 'Learn from the sun; it is warm to everyone, and is therefore never in short supply of those who adore it.', 5104, 0), (72419, 'The degree of loving is measured by the degree of giving.', 12361, 0), (72420, 'You know who you are, he said- that intimidates boys but oneday a man will come along and value that exact part in you. - Wise words from my best friend.', 3305, 0), (72421, 'Love is a two-way street, but not everyone deserves a license.', 5323, 0), (72422, 'A woman’s elegance will charm you for days,her beauty will charm you for weeks,her grace will charm you for years,and her virtue will charm you for a lifetime.', 5104, 0), (72423, 'If you kiss her cheeks, she is your friend; if you kiss her lips, she is your lover; if you kiss her heart, she is your soul mate.', 5104, 0), (72424, 'The greatest warriors fight not for crowns and splendor, but for love.', 5104, 0), (72425, 'Love rewards you more in a moment than pleasure could in a lifetime.', 5104, 0), (72426, 'Nothing can resist a person who is nonresistant... When you overcome negative with positive...hate with love... Evil with good. You''ve turn a loss to a win... You have become profound.', 8514, 0), (72427, 'For how could she dream for more when he was her every dream come true?', 15277, 0), (72428, 'Connect with someone on a deeper level…mentally, spiritually, emotionally…and your soul will transcend the height of ecstasy.', 5323, 0), (72429, 'To be fearlessly vulnerable with someone…One of the deepest, most desirable paradoxes of love.', 5323, 0), (72430, 'Love is everything, love is God in us. Love what you do, those you do it for, love others and yourself. Love is the key to success, prosperity and happiness. Give love always and you''ll never lack love.', 8514, 0), (72431, 'When a man meets the right woman, he meets a new strength!', 4606, 0), (72432, 'The best relationships are simple. No lies, no cheating, simply two people that will always be there for each other nomatter what.', 5485, 0), (72433, 'Love conquers the body by embracing it,conquers the mind by massaging it,conquers the heart by kissing it,and conquers the soul by marrying it.', 5104, 0), (72434, 'Though love may be blind, it sees much;though it may be deaf, it hears much;though it may be mute, it says much;and though it may be lame, it does much.', 5104, 0), (72435, 'I can’t quite figure out the difference between loving someone and loving things about them.', 7648, 0), (72436, 'I’ve become your heartbeat making you mine Upon every kiss of passion our souls shine', 2760, 0), (72437, 'The only thing I know for sure is that this summer, I want to be with you. Sometimes I wish I could make everything else go away and have it only be you and me in our own little world.', 11643, 0), (72438, 'I don’t have any fancy story,about the way we fell in love.It was that one awkward move,and the next I remember, I was looking at you.I don’t have any fancy allegory,about how we decided to marry,It was over the deck of that cruise,that you made an awkward move,And the next I remember, I conceived in your eye,some purer truth,and I was looking at you.I don’t have any fancy history,about how I know you so deeply,It always was that one awkward move,which I have trusted to pursue.Who said lovers are complex?All you need is their,one awkward move.Their soul in an instant,is engulfed,In that one tick of drool.That’s all what love is,that one awkward move,which is only meant only for you.', 2965, 0), (72439, 'Love is insanity, apparently.', 7648, 0), (72440, 'If people want to believe in Hollywood movies, let them believe in Hollywood movies. Being romantic is not a disease.', 12344, 0), (72441, 'While the world has found the right names for all chronic mental diseases, I believe poetry is also a brain dysfunction, yet the only one that owns itself the mastery for the cure. Isn’t it lovely to say, “He/She suffers of Poetry?”.', 12344, 0), (72442, 'There is truly no other place bearing so much love as airports.', 12344, 0), (72443, 'Love cannot exist without giving, however giving can exist without love.', 5805, 0), (72444, 'Her mouth connected with his. Everything inside her collapsed and was constructed, simultaneously.', 6846, 0), (72445, 'Love and pride will never dwell together, never ! Do not fool yourself, God and the devil will never share the same space. Therefore, drop your pride and experience love.', 5805, 0), (72446, 'Love is something you have or don’t have. Love is like a fever.', 7648, 0), (72447, 'It sounds like love just sort of happens, whether you want it to or not, whether you’re married or not.', 7648, 0), (72448, 'The only kind of love to be found, is within you. That other kind everybody wants... it finds you.', 2747, 0), (72449, 'The heart speaks when it is ready.....for love keeps no time.', 5641, 0), (72450, 'A boy who could make his mother feel special inspite of his own ordeals is the boon from God in lieu of some good deed.', 5414, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72451, 'The only regret I have is that I couldn''t teach you a lesson in humanity and humility. A mother should not depend on his son and that''s the one mistake I committed.', 5414, 0), (72452, 'The more silent you are at bed during times of crisis, the more are the chances of an amicable, dignified and a not so counterproductive interchange of romantic exuberance.', 5414, 0), (72453, 'Roses have thorns,’ we whine. When thorns of life entwine. Simple things can bring solace to heart-Things everyone take for granted-Like tending beds of fragile roses-with heart full of scars', 8514, 0), (72454, 'True love has no fear and similarly latter cannot have true love.', 5489, 0), (72455, 'Learn, Teach, Love, Experience and Grow. That''s what I know about this life we live.', 918, 0), (72456, 'Be like the sun who fell in love with the moon and shared all his light.', 3588, 0), (72457, 'A wanton women is ripened fruit,'' Constanze intoned,''begging to be plucked by the Goblin King.', 7592, 0), (72458, 'Don''t allow distance to truly separate you. Make your love last beyond the distance.', 15278, 0), (72459, 'Falling in love is accidental, staying in love is intentional, and growing in love is delightful.', 5104, 0), (72460, 'I need someone who knows to enjoy life. Someone who''ll get high with me at the Pere - Lechaise cemetery. Someone who''ll lose their breath running trough the Louvre. Someone who''ll go to coffee with a good book ( Fyodor Dostoyevsky, L. Tolstoy, Voltaire, A. Camus, Oscar Wilde, Gustave Flaubert ). During the weekends to the cafe de Flore, and after that lunch at Ritz. Someone who''ll get lost in Paris in the middle of the night. Someone who''ll lay beside Seine, drink wine and listen to Florence and Machine, Banks, Borns, Hurts, Bjork, Tom Odelle... Someone who can sit in front of S.Dali''s paintings for hours and not talk. Someone who wants to live. Someone who wants to travel and see the world. Someone who''ll look at the stars for hours, talk about life, someone who is not afraid of death.', 15279, 0), (72461, 'Remember, never give up on love. It is easier to give up in search of a better prize, because the brain always keeps craving for new stimulants, but this way you only keep on searching, never to find peace in love. Let me tell you a story. There was a student who asked his teacher, what is love. The teacher said go into the field and bring me the most beautiful flower. The student returned with no flower at hand andsaid, I found the most beautiful flower in the field but I didn''t pick it up for I might find a better one, but when I returned to the place, it was gone.We always look for the best in life. When we finally see it, we take it for granted and after some time start expecting a better one, not knowing that it''s the best. Seek for your love, and once you have it never ever give up on it, no matter the situations.', 2874, 0), (72462, 'A woman’s beauty is worth little to you, a woman’s intelligence is worth much to you, a woman’s virtue is worth more to you, a woman’s love is worth the most to you, and a woman’s loyalty is worth everything to you.', 5104, 0), (72463, 'Perhaps the most hillarious yet true advice I ever gave on marriage is this one. Don''t marry because of Love, marry because of food Love fades, beauty wanes but hungry doesn''t', 15280, 0), (72464, 'True love is like diamonds; scarce, and priceless.', 5104, 0), (72465, 'The greatest profit you make in business is not money, but happiness. The greatest riches you give in life are not possessions, but love. The greatest treasures you acquire in life are not jewels, but joy.', 5104, 0), (72466, 'Don’t say you’re sorry I have to let you go ….Time will show Sadness will grow …..', 15150, 0), (72467, 'Infinity and Always.', 15281, 0), (72468, 'When love invades your life, it captures your heart, imprisons your mind, and frees your soul.', 5104, 0), (72469, 'I never thought I would lose you I never thought You would be gone I never thought The love we had Now is done,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,You meant the world to me You are all I had in life My magical symphony Had ended tonight ………………………', 15150, 0), (72470, 'Start loving yourself early so others will know how to love you amazingly.', 15278, 0), (72471, 'He must be suffering, too. She had noted the weary sag of his shoulders, the quivering lips, the tear- filled eyes. Somehow she had never thought of him as hurting- of being capable of understanding how she felt.', 15282, 0), (72472, 'My name be Clark Davis", he hurried on,"an it peers to me thet you an'' me be in need of one another".', 15282, 0), (72473, 'Get up, work out, eat well, enjoy the moment, be present and show up for people who need your love; family, friends, less privileged, your followers. Appreciate love and remember, the journey is more important than the destination.', 8514, 0), (72474, 'When you are in love, your eyes see him only, your ears hear him only, your mouth speaks of him only, your mind thinks of him only, your heart desires him only, your soul lives for him only, and your entire universe is about him only.', 5104, 0), (72475, 'Love is the greatest drug; joy is the strongest medicine; virtue is the noblest remedy; together, they are the greatest therapy.', 5104, 0), (72476, 'When a woman misses you, you have her mind; when she cares for you, you have her heart, when she loves you, you have her soul.', 5104, 0), (72477, 'Marry the one who laughs when you laugh, and you are clever; marry the one who cries when you cry, and you are intelligent, but marry the one who does both with you, and you are wise.', 5104, 0), (72478, 'Without passion, the earth will be full of hollow bodies devoid of love, relationship, religion, art, science and technology', 8514, 0), (72479, 'Love is purely spiritual, until you can honestly accept and love your essence and truth, you have nothing to offer another', 8514, 0), (72480, 'Some relations just begin. Sometimes you need to but don’t want to make the first move. And you want to wait. I want to wait. Yes I want to. Why do some people suddenly come into your life out of nowhere and make a place in your heart? Its almost sacred or divine. And how do they? You want them to look at you and when they do, you don’t have the strength to look back. Why? You just feel too weak to look back. So is this love? But I want that strength inside me. And I know the person wants me too. But I am ready to wait. No hurry at all. Life is a paradox I know. And that’s very inviting.”A Novella, The Coffee and The Cola, Published 2016.', 15283, 0), (72481, 'Like freshly cut roses, I place life in a vase... of love.', 3588, 0), (72482, 'I long for you; I who usually longs without longing, as though I am unconscious and absorbed in neutrality and apathy, really, utterly long for every bit of you.', 629, 0), (72483, 'Like a child who saves their favourite food on the plate for last, I try to save all thoughts of you for the end of the day so I can dream with the taste of you on my tongue.', 3588, 0), (72484, 'I fell in loveand then I became love.', 3588, 0), (72485, 'Neither the secret whirring song of the stars nor the sonorous canticles of the earth knew the language that sprang up in the space between us. It was a dialect of heartbeats, strung together with the lilt of long suffering and the incandescent hope of an infinite future.', 7656, 0), (72486, 'The only thing that comes close to defining me correctly is my love.', 3588, 0), (72487, 'When the storm comes it is your soulmate who pulls out the umbrella and shelters you until the rainbow comes.', 5104, 0), (72488, 'Luke diagnosed himself to be in love, and sought no cure for the disease.', 9391, 0), (72489, 'When you are madly in love with someone, even when sanity tries to rescue you, you wrestle it.', 5104, 0), (72490, 'We cannot see love yet its nurturing warmth is the essence of our being and sorrow can touch our very soul. For remorse is like a ripple on the ocean, once given it remains only in the heart of the receiver.Believe in Yourself by Grace Willows', 7142, 0), (72491, 'Know that time is a balm that slowly heals all wound. You''ll heal, you''ll learn to live with the scars, you''ll love again and you won''t be the same, nor would you want to', 8514, 0), (72492, 'To this day when I inhale a light scent of Wrangler—its sweet sharpness—or the stronger, darker scent of Musk, I return to those hours and it ceases to be just cologne that I take in but the very scent of age, of youth at its most beautiful peak. It bears the memory of possibility, of unknown forests, unchartered territories, and a heart light and skipping, hell-bent as the captain of any of the three ships, determined at all costs to prevail to the new world. Turning back was no option. Whatever the gales, whatever the emaciation, whatever the casualty to self, onward I kept my course. My heart felt the magnetism of its own compass guiding me on—its direction constant and sure. There was no other way through. I feel it again as once it had been, before it was broken-in; its strength and resolute ardency. The years of solitude were nothing compared to what lay ahead. In sailing for the horizon that part of my life had been sealed up, a gentle eddy, a trough of gentle waves diminishing further, receding away. Whatever loneliness andpain went with the years between the ages of 14 and 20, was closed, irretrievable—I was already cast in form and direction in a certain course.When I open the little bottle of eau de toilette five hundred different days unfold within me, conversations so strained, breaking slowly, so painstakingly, to a comfortable place. A place so warm and inviting after the years of silence and introspect, of hiding. A place in the sun that would burn me alive before I let it cast a shadow on me. Until that time I had not known, I had not been conscious of my loneliness. Yes, I had been taciturn in school, alone, I had set myself apart when others tried to engage. But though I was alone, I had not felt the pangs of loneliness. It had not burdened or tormented as such when I first felt the clear tang of its opposite in the form of another’s company. Of Regn’s company. We came, each in our own way, in our own need—listening, wanting, tentatively, as though we came upon each other from the side in spite of having seen each other head on for two years. It was a gradual advance, much again like a vessel waiting for its sails to catch wind, grasping hold of the ropes and learning much too quickly, all at once, how to move in a certain direction. There was no practicing. It was everything and all—for the first and last time. Everything had to be right, whether it was or not. The waters were beautiful, the work harder than anything in my life, but the very glimpse of any tempest of defeat was never in my line of vision. I’d never failed at anything. And though this may sound quite an exaggeration, I tell you earnestly, it is true. Everything to this point I’d ever set my mind to, I’d achieved. But this wasn’t about conquering some land, nor had any of my other desires ever been about proving something. It just had to be—I could not break, could not turn or retract once I’d committed myself to my course. You cannot force a clock to run backwards when it is made to persevere always, and ever, forward. Had I not been so young I’d never have had the courage to love her.', 15284, 0), (72493, 'Every morningbefore the birds starttrilling me their stories,I give birth to a new lovethrough my same old heartwhen a lake’s placidityfinds life in the swans breathOnly for you...From the poem ''Only For You', 2760, 0), (72494, 'Thorns with rose petals, beauty with imperfection, softness of insensibility, pain of love; duality of human nature', 8514, 0), (72495, 'If love weighs you downand casts a shadow on your lifethen it isn’t love.Love is light and makes you light.', 3588, 0), (72496, 'For Past is never buried-It just shines with a brighter ray,Perhaps because now we look at it as a third personUshering in a smile with moist eyes Which is but a reflection of an array of infinite emotions.Indeed, Past is never buried-It breathes silently,Deep inside,Distant yet alive.', 6425, 0), (72497, 'Endeavor to do what you love so that your work becomes an expression of love to the world', 8514, 0), (72498, 'Celebrate differences, give love, and more love. Anything short is a rigidity that cuts both ways and spawns odium and ire', 8514, 0), (72499, 'Love can make you blind Love can make you see Many things around you It’s a fancy …………………………….Love can make you Feel like dying Love can keeps you alive …………..Love can drive you crazy Only few survives ………………….', 15150, 0), (72500, 'It is hard to love yourself if you never spend time with yourself. ''Alone Time'' is Necessary', 4554, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72501, 'Love is a place of rest, a place of comfort and a place of peace and enjoyment.', 4587, 0), (72502, 'A genuine love gives it all, it protects and no strings attached. Love someone today.', 4587, 0), (72503, 'Love should be a 365 days dose not some occasional yearly event. Happy New Year 2017.', 4587, 0), (72504, 'Love = Living Onwardly Victoriously Eternally', 3801, 0), (72505, 'Never settle for being ordinary, you''re made whole in God, you''re uniquely perfect. Made to love and be loved.', 8514, 0), (72506, 'I don’t know what else to do You’re always on my mind You’re the curse of my life I can’t describe,,,,,,,,,,,,,,You hurt my heart For so long You made a fool Out of me …….Now you’re wishing to be My destiny………………..Go away I had enough of you……Just go away You’re selfish You know it too…I had enough of you eternally…………………..', 15150, 0), (72507, 'You really shouldn''t say I love you unless you mean it. But if you mean it you should say it a lot. People forget.', 1471, 0), (72508, 'A bird, unable to fly, is still a bird; but a human unable to love is an inexpensive stone: like a piece of uric acid stone', 2760, 0), (72509, 'When you look into your soulmates eyes, you see the world; into your soulmates heart, you see the sky, and into your soulmates soul, you see the universe.', 5104, 0), (72510, 'If love happens because of a reason then the same love will disappear for another reason.', 15285, 0), (72511, 'Love at first sight? Let me just put on my glasses.', 6269, 0), (72512, 'The word of God says "God is love", implying to love others is to reveal God to them.', 5805, 0), (72513, 'You are my first and last light,of my day and my night.', 7108, 0), (72514, 'Moments of love and compassion are the only immortal moments in human being’s life! We humans are mortals with immortal moments!', 3701, 0), (72515, 'Falling in love with a woman’s body is lust, with a woman’s mind is sense, with a woman’s heart is virtue, and with a woman’s soul is wisdom.', 5104, 0), (72516, 'At all times we are either in fear or we are in love. We are either open or we are closed. Expansive or contracted.', 4609, 0), (72517, 'Love at first life!', 6269, 0), (72518, 'Love is all, what you put into it.!', 10372, 0), (72519, 'Wipe those tears, as they have cleansed your soul.', 15286, 0), (72520, 'A person''s disposition should serve as a narrative of their lives not the pigmentation of their skin.', 8517, 0), (72521, 'LOVE— yes, that one never fails!', 7664, 0), (72522, 'Love requires commitment, flexibility, transparency and loyalty. Happy Valentines Day 2017.', 4587, 0), (72523, 'To love someone is to give her or him your entire heart and she or he should give that love back to you 100% as well. That''s called two way street relationship. Happy Valentines Day 2017.', 4587, 0), (72524, 'If you have money, you are affluent; if you have joy, you are wealthy; and if you have love, you are rich.', 5104, 0), (72525, 'The sun was shining bright The moon is crying tonight I miss you I miss your eyes tonight ……………', 15150, 0), (72526, 'If you come away with me, I can promise you pain and disgrace,” I said. “But I will love you like no other can.', 15287, 0), (72527, 'If you love two people at the same time, choose the second one, because if you really loved the first one, you wouldn’t have fallen for the second.', 15288, 0), (72528, 'Love is fierce like a lion; once it has entered the heart, it is in vain to resist.', 5104, 0), (72529, 'Being deeply, passionately, and intensely in love is being deeply, passionately, and intensely in life.', 3588, 0), (72530, 'I’m a winner because I always bet on you.', 3588, 0), (72531, 'I was mistaken when I said you live in my heart. How absurd I was when you live in my fingertips so that everything I touch is you. How foolish I was when you live in my toes so that everywhere I go there''s you. How senseless of me to say you live in my heart when you breathe in my lungs, walk on my mind, and drink in my mouth. I came to pen another poem for you, but even every unwritten poem is you.', 3588, 0), (72532, 'I feel your words on my lipsand feel your mood in my hips', 7249, 0), (72533, 'I write because the security of your love allows me to develop my craft without concerning myself with trivialities — as if your love could be any more complete. But I write, in the first place,because of you, my muse. I write for your green eyes to glance at my humble words and for the pleasure of hearing you utter them.', 3588, 0), (72534, 'You are my favourite part of life.', 3588, 0), (72535, 'Love is the only brick that hits you on the head and gives you a smile instead of tears.', 5104, 0), (72536, 'Love isn’t blind. Maybe we are all born blind and love finally gives us sight.', 3588, 0), (72537, 'I love you so much I want to share youwith yourself.I know you do not insist that I do, but I love you so much I want to shareGod with you.', 3588, 0), (72538, 'Love is more powerful than even the sun; light can only enter your eyes, but love can enter your soul.', 5104, 0), (72539, 'Love makes you strong when others are weak, brave when others are scared, hopeful when others are despairing and cheerful when others are sad.', 5104, 0), (72540, 'If you want to make your wife joyful, treat her like Holy Spirit', 5805, 0), (72541, 'How is it possible, you ask, for love to be greater than the person who does the loving? That’s because love defies the rules of reason. It is the only exception.', 3588, 0), (72542, 'I came to pen another poem for you, but even every unwritten poem is you.', 3588, 0), (72543, 'I knew I loved you when the very thought of breaking your heart, broke mine.', 15289, 0), (72544, 'Don’t say to yourself, ‘Everyone argues!’ to justify and normalise your fighting, when the most natural thing is to love.', 3588, 0), (72545, 'No three words have greater force than “I want you,” greater strength than “I need you,” greater might than “I miss you,” and greater power than “I love you.', 5104, 0), (72546, 'Joy is the best companion, virtue is the noblest acquaintance, wisdom is the cleverest friend, and love is the kindest soul mate.', 5104, 0), (72547, 'I searched for love, and only found God; I searched for God, and only found love.', 5104, 0), (72548, 'Even if love were considered a mental illness, that would not prevent it from being a pleasant one.', 5104, 0), (72549, 'I don''t believe in your version of love, I have my own', 15290, 0), (72550, 'If you have her mind, you have her for a moment; if you have her heart, you have her for a while; if you have her soul, you have her for a lifetime.', 5104, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72551, '2. A heart broken by a girl can be repaired by another girl only.', 6347, 0), (72552, 'What about those Promises of yours to never leave me? she asked, stammering too much this time. His cruel smirk was as gut-wrenching as his words— Promises are meant to be broken, sweetheart.', 7668, 0), (72553, 'One joke is enough to put a smile on your face.One hug is enough to put a smile on your heart.One kiss is enough to put a smile on your soul.', 5104, 0), (72554, 'Marry someone you can live with, and you have found your companion; marry someone you can’t live without, and you have found your soulmate.', 5104, 0), (72555, 'If you have to love, then love greatly.', 12555, 0), (72556, 'If you love and care enough, you will give a lot, you will forgive a lot.', 5521, 0), (72557, 'The way your curious eyes were chasing mine when I stood in front of you, I knew I had known these eyes before.', 7668, 0), (72558, 'You know what, the moment I see you, first thing that comes to my mind is, I have just wasted 26 years of my life without you...', 15291, 0), (72559, 'I feel the pain—everywhere.', 7668, 0), (72560, 'Do not delude yourself, tomorrow is not guaranteed; and even if good fortune brings you your tomorrow, there is no guarantee those you love will be a part of it. Do not squander your precious, limited time. Value what love you have in your life - nothing is more valuable. Make it known to those who matter.', 5027, 0), (72561, 'The most valuable real estate in the universe is inside your soul.', 5104, 0), (72562, 'Life is one big gym where we need to constantly workout to stay fit for this world. And indeed love here is the treadmill.', 2760, 0), (72563, 'It is easier to wipe a thousand tears from your eyes than to wipe a single tear from your soul.', 5104, 0), (72564, 'Oceanic farness treasures tomorrowMingled tears lost in the sea of sorrowOur immortal love will lead us a way When pale days remain cloudy and grey', 2760, 0), (72565, 'What if the door you love is locked and cannot be open? The answer is very simple: Find another door!', 3701, 0), (72566, 'I threw myself so far in your depth that it took me a month to come out and notice I was actually sitting in my room. Nowhere else. Not with you.', 7668, 0), (72567, 'Someday, even my existence would be felt.', 7668, 0), (72568, 'Do you love me enough that I am allowedto be damaged? Do you love me enough that I am allowed to be weak in some places?', 7668, 0), (72569, 'When two souls are united as one the universe itself is powerless to separate them.', 5104, 0), (72570, 'I saw spark in your eyes while you chose only flaws in me, that made the difference!', 12721, 0), (72571, 'There''s nothing that''s eternally satisfying except unconditional love.', 5546, 0), (72572, 'I am saving my love in four parts. One part I will give to my family, because they give life to me. One part I will give to my future husband, because he will be the one who I will accompany with me for the rest of the life. The third part I will give to my husband''s family, because if it was not for his mother and father I would not have him. The fourth part I give to myself, because if a woman does not love herself, how she could love another?', 15292, 0), (72573, 'I would die for you, my love—in old age.', 6269, 0), (72574, 'Love begins with the stage of subconscious primitive lust and attraction. I’m saying primitive because at this very early stage there is really no difference between primitive man and modern man.', 2874, 0), (72575, 'For despite what some people say, love is not only a sweet falling bound to come and quickly go away.', 190, 0), (72576, 'Sometimes the bravest thing you can do is let someone love you.', 15293, 0), (72577, 'Love is love, even if it is illicit; like light remains light even in the darkness.', 2760, 0), (72578, 'I read old poems I wrote. They were all about you.', 15294, 0), (72579, 'When love enters your heart, hate is given an eviction notice.', 5104, 0), (72580, 'Never chase people. Be you and the right people who belong in your life and deserve a place in your heart will come, find and appreciate you!', 7682, 0), (72581, 'Beauty catches your eye, joy seizes your heart, and love captures your soul.', 5104, 0), (72582, 'If you put all of your eggs in love’s basket, joy will hatch.', 5104, 0), (72583, 'I still think about you at nightyou come back to me with the stars.', 5156, 0), (72584, 'Love is a divine lullaby', 15295, 0), (72585, 'If you wake with a change of direction, deciding you hate who you''ve been,Remember, I loved you every yesterday as I will continue to love you then.Whomever person you become I shall worship and whatever path you pave I will follow,Because I loved you every yesterday and I will love you every tomorrow.', 8918, 0), (72586, 'A man can deceive a women, so can a woman deceive a man; but if both are deceived its LOVE!', 12721, 0), (72587, 'Many people in life will catch your eye, but few will catch your heart. Make sure you notice the difference.', 5485, 0), (72588, 'If someone is destined to be with you, nothing can keep her away; if she is not, nothing can make her stay.', 5104, 0), (72589, 'When the head tries to rule the heart, emotion poisons it.', 5104, 0), (72590, 'He kissed her so gently she wondered if she had imagined it', 21, 0), (72591, 'We''d rather have a grand spectacle of retribution of the ''wicked'', than their silent walk towards redemption that our wishes questions the depth and nature of our love and hearts.', 10976, 0), (72592, 'The lessons of relationship that our primordial ancestors learned are deeply encoded in the genetics of our neurobiological circuits of love. They are present from the moment we are born and activated at puberty by the cocktail of neurochemicals. It’s an elegant synchronized system. At first our brain weighs a potential partner, and if the person ﬁts our ancestral wish list, we get a spike in the release of sex chemicals that makes us dizzy with a rush of unavoidable infatuation. It’s the ﬁrst step down the primeval path of pair-bonding.', 2874, 0), (72593, 'Males of all species are made for wooing females, and females typically choose among their suitors. If you take a closer look, you can observe such behavior all around you. The beautiful bird chirping outside your window. It’s a mating call. That pretty little bird is trying to attract a potential mate, so that it can propagate its genes. Why does the peacock have such beautiful feathers? It is to attract a healthy female. He as well is trying to propagate his genes. Even we humans, are not much different from the rest of the animal kingdom when it comes to attracting potential mates. When women dress up for their night out at the club, they are doing so to look attractive. This is a subconscious evolutionary desire to attract as many potential mates as possible.... While women tend to grab attention with their looks, men on the other hand, tend to attract as many potential females as possible, by showing off their resources. When a man shows off with his fancy car, expensive gold watch and suit, or flexes his muscles and brags about how many credit cards he owns, he’s doing so to make himself desirable by healthy women, in order to propagate his genes. It is all in the pursuit of reproduction.', 2874, 0), (72594, 'In the beginning of our love lives, it is the beastly instinct of sexual attraction that drives us all. The butterflies in your stomach simply signal your mind that the person in front of you would make a fantastic mate to make babies with. Without this primeval drive, you won’t ever fall for anyone in your entire lifetime. The very attraction you feel towards a person in a romantic way, is a mental manifestation of a subconscious desire to mate with that person.', 2874, 0), (72595, 'Let’s talk about mankind’s most adored emotion – Love. However, love itself is not a single emotion, rather a blend of many. It is such an enchanting sensation, that it has been inspiring artists, scientists, philosophers and thinkers for ages. Albert Einstein said, “any man who can drive safely while kissing a pretty girl is simply not giving the kiss the attention it deserves”. Geniuses around the world came up with various creations under the spell of love. Schrodinger’s Wave Equation, Hawking’s Hawking Radiation, Tagore’s songs, Rumi’s poems, are just a few among the plethora of scientific and philosophical literature created under the enigmatic and warm influence of love. So, technically it is totally worth being crazy in love.', 2874, 0), (72596, 'Were my love the sky, it would be boundless.Were my love the sea, it would be ceaseless.Were my love the world, it would be limitless.Were my love the universe, it would be endless.', 5104, 0), (72597, 'By the time you become an expert at marriage, it is too late to start a new one.', 5104, 0), (72598, 'Treat marriage like a diamond necklace; if broken, fix it, but do not throw it away.', 5104, 0), (72599, 'There is a natural magic in the feeling of love that has been nourished by Mother Nature through millions of years. It can make you reach the zenith of your true potential. It can awaken your mind towards your deepest powers, and make you endowed with tools of greatness that you can never access in an ordinary state of mind.', 2874, 0), (72600, 'At that very first kiss of my life I felt something melt inside me that hurt in an exquisite way. All my longings, all my dreams and sweet anguish, all the secrets that slept deep within my limbic brain came awake. I felt billions of Beach Boys playing their sweet melody inside my heart in perfect harmony with the universe.', 2874, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (72601, 'We were the only two people in the entire airport who lost total track of time, for we were consumed by space-time at that present moment. Time was irrelevant to our existence, for we didn’t want to exist outside the tight and glorious knots of each other’s arms. Time is basically an illusion created by the mind to aid in our sense of temporal presence in the vast ocean of space. Without the neurons to create a virtual perception of the past and the future based on all our experiences, there is no actual existence of the past and the future. All that there is, is the present.', 2874, 0), (72602, 'Nature programmed the neurobiological processes of early love to appear as something beyond the primitive sexual cravings of the genitals. So, from an evolutionary standpoint, it all leads to copulation and reproduction, but from the perspective of the individual who has recently fallen head over heels in love with someone, it is mostly about a sensation of warmth and delight, and rarely of sexual nature.', 2874, 0), (72603, 'Speak to me: I will spend my lifetime trying to understand you.', 3588, 0), (72604, 'We start a relationship with someone not only because of how great they are but how great they make us feel. And because they have granted us this extraordinary gift—a chance to experience love, joy, compassion, and security —it is our exclusive privilege to make them feel wonderful about themselves, especially during days when they, themselves, don''t feel so wonderful.', 3588, 0), (72605, 'You make me feel like a firefly. Trapped in a belljar', 15296, 0), (72606, 'Love is more potent than wine', 15297, 0), (72607, 'There are two kinds of diamonds in this world: The diamond itself and the eyes full of love!', 3701, 0), (72608, 'It’s natural to want someone you love to do what you want, or what you think would be good for them, but you have to let everything happen to them. You can’t interfere with people you love any more than you’re supposed to interfere with people you don’t even know. And that’s hard. Because you often feel like interfering—you want to be the one who makes the plans. . . You can’t protect people, kiddo, all you can do is love them.', 850, 0), (72609, 'I have the ‘L’.You have the ‘O’.Fate has the ‘V’.Together we have the ‘E’.How then can we deny we are in LOVE?', 5104, 0), (72610, 'Like any / unloved thing, I don’t know if I’m real /when I’m not being touched.', 15298, 0), (72611, 'To ease a grieving heart is the world''s greatest pleasure, more so, when the heart is yours.', 15014, 0), (72612, 'There is no gem like virtue, no wealth like happiness, no treasure like faith, and no jewel like love.', 5104, 0), (72613, 'The greatest gift you can give to someone is your heart; because when you give your heart, you are giving your most prized possession.', 5104, 0), (72614, 'Love has the mind of a sage, the heart of a saint, and the soul of an angel.', 5104, 0), (72615, 'If your wife puts on ten pounds, love her ten times more.If she puts on a hundred pounds, love her a hundred times more.If she puts on a thousand pounds, love her a thousand times more.', 5104, 0), (72616, 'Be still my hand and let the words write themselves upon my heart. Be still my heart and let your pages be filled in silence.', 8596, 0), (72617, 'Every time I see you I fall in love all over again.', 15299, 0), (72618, 'Girlfriend is injurious to health...!!!', 8534, 0), (72619, 'We can''t escape the need to loveNorCan we resist the longing to be loved', 15300, 0), (72620, 'There''s a kind of purity to a relationship unencumbered by convention, a sense of simplicity and freedom.', 12116, 0), (72621, 'Love is not sacrificing for each other, but helping each other to become more unified - Mentally by respecting each other''s EGO; Psychologically - by understanding and overcoming the subtle nuances of the mind that are detrimental to each other''s progress and Spiritually - becoming one with the cosmic whole. This organic growth in all sphere of life is what we call LOVE! Have you experienced this?', 12721, 0), (72622, 'You were my marital bliss,” he said to me this morning. “You can be again!” You know what I answered? “A marital blister, that’s what we’ll have if I stay.', 15301, 0), (72623, 'Beds ain''t for sleeping, and clothes ain''t for bed.', 15302, 0), (72624, 'Lust makes you weak, passion makes you strong, love makes you brave, and heartache makes you wise.', 5104, 0), (72625, 'Women are like shadows; when you chase them, they run from you; when you run from them, they chase you.', 5104, 0), (72626, 'Love is the world’s greatest doctor', 15303, 0), (72627, 'I look into your eyes and I’m sure that some divine artist dipped her brush in the same soul and used it to paint us both.', 8596, 0), (72628, 'I love you. There is no limit to what I can give to you, no time I need. Even when this world is a forgotten whisper of dust between the stars, I will love you.', 343, 0), (72629, 'He is the greatest mystery I had even known, one that always had me craving just a little bit more.', 3305, 0), (72630, 'I would fight dragons, I would walk over flaming coals, I would enter the Valley of the Dead, if I thought I might have a chance of your heart.', 11190, 0), (72631, 'I share my secrets with the moon, She talks about her love story with the sun & I share all my dreams about you.', 3305, 0), (72632, 'I am your earth if you want me to be.I am your sky if you want me to be.I am your sun if you want me to be.I am your world if you want me to be.I am your universe if you want me to be.', 5104, 0), (72633, 'When you are in love, your eyes see him only, your ears hear him only, your mouth speaks of him only, your mind thinks of him only, your heart desires him only, your soul lives for him only; your entire universe revolves around him only.', 5104, 0), (72634, 'Love is a combination of friendship, passion, and respect.', 14739, 0), (72635, 'Love is a spirit, and therefore cannot die a natural death.', 5104, 0), (72636, 'False love can be bought', 15304, 0), (72637, 'Love only knocks on your heart’s door when certain it has the right address.', 5104, 0), (72638, 'All that two lovers want, is to be one with the other in a moment of ecstasy.', 2874, 0), (72639, 'Through sexual intimacy, two human beings become one mind, body and soul wrapped up in the cocoon of their skin.', 2874, 0), (72640, 'Love can literally transform a human being. It can make us do either heroic or evil deeds. It is the best inspiration ever.', 2874, 0), (72641, 'I wanna let you know you''re all I need tonight every time I see you I wish to hold you tight ............you''re everything for me you''re always crossing my mind each and every night I Wanna be by your side ..........', 15150, 0), (72642, '[We learn] from heartbreak that love is not for idealists, but realists; it should always be passionate, but it is always dangerous. That infatuation is a game of power, but love leaves us powerless--and it is our dignity in its aftermath that defines us.', 15305, 0), (72643, 'I miss you,” is how she entices you.“I want you,” is how she charms you.“I need you,” is how she entraps you.“I love you,” is how she imprisons you.', 5104, 0), (72644, 'The heart is a wanderer, the mind is its map; love is its destination.', 5104, 0), (72645, 'Passion stimulates you, love intoxicates you, marriage sobers you, and parenthood tries you.', 5104, 0), (72646, 'The very first few days when you actually start having symptoms of falling for someone special, are the days of heavenly bliss and unreasonable madness.', 2874, 0), (72647, 'A life without having loved someone is a life never lived.', 2874, 0), (72648, 'Sometimes all you need is someone who is willing to listen to you without advising or judging you.', 5414, 0), (72649, 'Love makes you the richest person in the world, no matter how poor you are.', 5104, 0), (72650, 'I''ve a very simple yet powerful prese